  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to assess the clinical effectiveness of Fentanyl ETHYPHARM when
      used to relieve breakthrough pain (BTP) in opioid-treated cancer patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
